casebody.data:
Washington Mutual Bank, fka Washington Mutual Bank, FA v. Beatley et al., Appellants; Federal Deposit Insurance Corporation, Receiver, Appellee.

[Cite as Washington Mat. Bank v. Beatley, 122 Ohio St.3d 1212, 2009-Ohio-2611.]

(No. 2008-1056 Submitted May 19, 2009 Decided June 10, 2009.) Taft, Stettinius & Hollister, L.L.P., Charles A. Bowers, and Gregory J. O’Brien, for appellee. Kevin E. Humphreys, for appellants.

{¶ 1} The cause is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently certified.

Moyer, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, and Cupp, JJ., concur.
